author: Spencer Perry
title: First Look at Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt Season 3
text:
SHARE First look at Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt Season 3 
Netflix has debuted the first photos from the upcoming Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt Season 3 which you can check out in the gallery below! In addition, the extensive list of guest stars has been announced for the third season and includes Laura Dern, Daveed Diggs, Rachel Dratch, Ray Liotta, Andrea Martin and Maya Rudolph, with returning guest stars Fred Armisen, Anna Camp, Mike Carlsen, Josh Charles, David Cross, Tina Fey, Jon Hamm and Amy Sedaris. Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt Season 3 premieres Friday, May 19 only on Netflix. 
In the Season 3 premiere, Kimmy finds herself in an unfamiliar position with the Reverend back in her life. Titus returns from his cruise and auditions for an exciting new role. Lillian has to break up with her boyfriend Robert Durst. 
Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt was created by Tina Fey ( 30 Rock ) and Robert Carlock ( 30 Rock ), who serve as executive producers with Jeff Richmond ( 30 Rock ) and David Miner ( 30 Rock , Brooklyn Nine-Nine ). Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt is a production of Universal Television, Little Stranger Inc., 3 Arts Entertainment and Bevel Gears for Netflix.
